Log:
  Fix RPC headers for C++

  C++ mangling will cause trouble with variables like __rpc_xdr
  in xdr.h so rename this to XDR.
  While here add proper C++ guards to RPC headers.

  PR:		137443
  MFC after:	2 weeks

